############################################################
### The perfect golang .gitignore
############################################################
#### Recursively ignore EVERYTHING!
/**

#### Still descend into directories
!*/

#### Dont ignore these patterns
# Duh!
!.gitignore

## go files
!*.go
!*.gotext
!*.gohtml
!go.mod
!go.sum

## Proto files
!*.proto

## sql files
!*.sql

## Dockerfiles
!Dockerfile
!Dockerfile.*

## Markdown docs
!*.md

## Get templates in there.
!*.tpl
!*.tmpl
!*.tstext

## TypeScript client
!*.ts
!*.json
ts/client/node_modules/
ts/client/dist/
dist/

## yaml
!*.yaml
!*.yml

## OpenTofu / Terraform
!*.tf
!*.tfvars
!*.hcl
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
# Real var files carry secrets / personal config — only the
# *.example.tfvars templates are committed.
deploy/**/terraform.tfvars
deploy/**/*.auto.tfvars
# State files: bootstrap runs with local state and other invocations may
# produce non-default state filenames (state.json, state.<env>.json) that
# slip past the generic *.tfstate rules above.
deploy/**/state.json
#deploy/**/state.*.json
#deploy/**/*.tfstate*

## GitHub config
!CODEOWNERS

##### End dont ignore

#vendor/

#.idea/
